data.enText: a common freshwater fish that is used for food. There are several types of trout .
Shall we have trout for dinner?

tr: any of various game and food fishes of cool fresh waters mostly smaller than typical salmons
flesh of any of several primarily freshwater game and food fishes

value.def: A trout is a fairly large fish that lives in rivers and streams.

posc.def: Trout is this fish eaten as food.
